io.realm.dynamic

Class DynamicRealmList

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
      • java.util.AbstractList<DynamicRealmObject>
        • io.realm.dynamic.DynamicRealmList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<DynamicRealmObject>, java.util.Collection<DynamicRealmObject>, java.util.List<DynamicRealmObject>

    public class DynamicRealmList
extends java.util.AbstractList<DynamicRealmObject>
    RealmList exposed using a dynamic API. All objects in the list must have the same schema even though they are accessed dynamically. Null values are not allowed in this list.
